WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.033 --> 00:00:03.399
Dobrodošli v Precision Imaging
Network, delu rešitve Microsoft for

2
00:00:03.399 --> 00:00:06.766
Health Precision Imaging. Precision
Imaging Network uporablja zmogljive

3
00:00:06.766 --> 00:00:10.133
modele UI tretjih oseb, ki radiologom
pomagajo pri interpretaciji slik in

4
00:00:10.133 --> 00:00:13.500
