5
00:00:15.466 --> 00:00:18.439
The Precision Imaging Network deluje s
storitvami PowerShare Image Sharing,

6
00:00:18.439 --> 00:00:21.412
PowerScribe One in mPower Clinical
Analytics za prikazovanje ključnih

7
00:00:21.412 --> 00:00:24.385
